{"tid":1015973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獅城豪放女只穿絲質睡衣上街　網友：真是清涼過了頭！","createTime":"2019-02-10T13:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T08:32:44.000Z","uid":2644,"like":246,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"bb416bbe5a253733a81002ebb7cf2c4253bba6f8","tid":1015973,"uid":2644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:20:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">豪放女只穿絲質睡衣上街<br />\n胸前兩點若隱若現<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Eqp8bnT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEqp8bnT.png&h=63de83e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡1名女子，近日僅僅穿了絲質背心型睡衣，裡面什麼都沒有穿，就跑到公共場所的<br />\n自動提款機提錢，被網友拍了上網分享，網友都說真是清涼過了頭！ <br />\n<br />\n由照片來看，這位豪放女子年約30歲，穿著1雙拖鞋，胸前兩點「呼之欲出」，胸口與手<br />\n臂部分，由於開口很大，也露出多處肌膚，而背心長度也僅僅遮住臀部。 <br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞《中國報》報導，地點應是新加坡烏節索美塞地鐵站，當地資深律師表示，這名<br />\n女子的行為「處於灰色地帶」，如果有民眾不爽報警投訴，才有可能被當成「公共滋擾」<br />\n或「裸露」案件處理。 <br />\n<br />\n這名律師也說：「當然如果她公然裸露、或在地鐵站公然拉客，就另當別論，因為這就一<br />\n定是犯法的」。 <br />\n<br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9556ff410b5781d038e8e0fe1e1acdf41a3d3b","tid":1015973,"uid":160095,"like":430,"dislike":27,"score":403,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:27:50.000Z","msg":"條女好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adde54b367a8412692d7f8f504f0ff2b7b0af2de","tid":1015973,"uid":54472,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:35:40.000Z","msg":"第一張就望緊鏡頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b14ed46c0e5bae6f315ccdea63560cd124bf128","tid":1015973,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0ed855043fcb8f0de51a3d86d0a6b80561e7bab","tid":1015973,"uid":90601,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T13:44:14.000Z","msg":"馬拉樣"},{"pid":"2b800a0af08bdeb